## 3. Dashboard Tab

### 3.1 Purpose
At-a-glance summary of the group's (Admin) or the member's own (Member) financial health.

### 3.2 Metrics / Widgets
| Widget | Definition | Admin scope | Member scope |
|---|---|---|---|
| Revenue to Date | Sum of all confirmed payments received | All members | Own payments only |
| Payments Not Yet Confirmed | Count of pending payments vs. total expected payments this cycle, shown as `X / Y` | All members | Own only |
| Harvest Released to Date | Count of harvests released vs. total harvests due, shown as `X of Y` | All members | Own only |
| Active Users vs Invited | Count of active accounts vs. total invited accounts | All members (admin only widget) | N/A — hide for member |
| Total Revenue | Cumulative total across all time | All members | Own only |

### 3.3 Charts
- A **bar/line chart** showing revenue (or contributions) by month, with a **Year selector** (Jan–Dec) to filter the chart to a chosen calendar year.
- A **Users chart/widget** showing user growth or active-vs-invited breakdown over time (admin only).
- All chart data must be filterable by year using the year selector control shown in the mockup.

### 3.4 Currency
- Amounts formatted with the configured currency symbol (default £), 2 decimal places.

