## 6. Notification Tab

### 6.1 Purpose
Central feed of notifications/messages related to:
- Savings commitments **requested** (e.g., "Request Collection Month" submissions)
- Commitments **being processed** (e.g., payment confirmation pending)
- Commitments **accepted/confirmed**

### 6.2 Requirements
- Chronological list (most recent first), read/unread state.
- Members see only notifications relevant to them; Admins see notifications across all members (or a filtered admin feed — confirm with client whether admin notification feed should include every member event or just ones requiring admin action).
- Clicking a notification should deep-link to the relevant record (e.g., the Savings Commitment row or Submitted Request).

