## 12. Notifications & Emails

### 12.1 Email Triggers
| Trigger | Recipient(s) | Content |
|---|---|---|
| Member added via "Save" | Admin + New Member | Registration/welcome notice, no login link |
| Member added via "Save and Invite" | Admin + New Member | Welcome message + unique tokenized invite link to set password and log in |
| Send Reminder (manual, admin-triggered) | Selected Member | Reminder about a specific savings commitment |
| Request Collection Month submitted | Admin (and/or Member, confirm) | Notification that a collection month request needs action |
| Payment Confirmed | Member | Confirmation that their payment was recorded |
| Harvest Released | Member | Confirmation that their harvest/payout was released |

### 12.2 In-App Notifications
- Mirror key email events as entries in the Notification Tab (Section 6) so users don't have to rely solely on email.

